<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.9">
<l>kōṭṭumaṇ koṇṭiṭantu kuṭaṅkaiyilmaṇ koṇṭaḷantu</l>
<l>mīṭṭuma tuṇṭumiḻntu viḷaiyāṭuvi malaṉmalai</l>
<l>yīṭṭiya palporuḷka ḷempirāṉoṭa ṭiyuṟaiyeṉṟu</l>
<l>ōṭṭarun taṇcilampā ṟuṭaimāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the spotless one who played at</l>
<l rend="indent">digging up and taking the earth with [his] tusks,</l>
<l rend="indent">measuring and taking the earth in the palm of [his] hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] consuming and spitting it out again</l>
<l>that is Māliruñcōlai with the cool Cilampu River</l>
<l rend="indent">which comes running with offerings</l>
<l rend="indent">of many gathered treasures for our Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
